{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act30side", "eventName": "銀心湖列車", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "RS-2", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "同車異圖", "storyInfo": "子爵放心不下“灰禮帽”，前去尋找，卻撞見“灰禮帽”與鐧“對峙”的一幕，他立即判斷情勢不妙，轉身就跑，鐧緊跟其後。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g3_traincarriage", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_trainlp", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$comedy_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……就是說那個蜂蜜飲料啊，喝起來甜滋滋的，沒想到後勁大得很！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過對我來說也就一般般啦，我朋友還說我醉蜜，結果呢，我精神得很，她倒是先倒下了。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？喂喂，大叔？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂——你在聽嗎——", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "哈洛德", "content": "嗯……"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#16$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "哈洛德", "content": "啊？"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恕我失禮，羅莎琳，你剛剛說什麼？", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#16$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說我朋友醉蜜！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，是的是的，沒錯，醉蜜。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嘖，真麻煩……", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大叔你要是有什麼在意的事，就先去解決一下吧。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在這副魂不守舍的樣子，根本沒法聊。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不，現在可沒有什麼比羅莎琳你的故事更值得我在意的。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續說說醉蜜的事吧，羅莎琳，我記得列車上應該也有賣含蜂蜜的特產飲料。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，少騙人。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這雙眼睛利著呢，從剛剛那個戴帽子的傢伙來開始，大叔你就不太對勁了。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們是朋友……不對，我看不像。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#7$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就是仇人？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這倒也稱不上。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許用“同僚”勉強能概括我與那位先生的關係，儘管我們在“公司”內並非隸屬同一部門。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，那就是休假時撞見關係不怎麼樣的同事。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我喜歡這個說法。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，羅莎琳，我承認我有點擔心我的同僚能否順利完成他的工作，所以，原諒我要失陪一會。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為補償，我會給你帶蜂蜜飲料，主要原料是謝拉格特產高地蜂蜜，每一滴都是耶拉岡德的恩賜，天然純淨……", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的？但我已經要對這套耶拉岡德廣告詞無感了……", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#6$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "千真萬確。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過你的朋友說你會醉蜜，我想我們需要做個約定——每天最多一瓶，以防你在旅行期間真的喝醉。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g2_trainwalkway", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_trainlp", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們之間沒有如此劍拔弩張的必要，鐧女士。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵閣下心繫喀蘭貿易，同時也關注謝拉格的發展，為其留意謝拉格的方方面面，是我的工作。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次自然也不例外，您不必如此防範。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的工作，包括參觀列車的包廂？", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的變化驚人，不是嗎？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據我所知，這條從聖山腳下到銀心湖的線路上，投入使用的列車都是自維多利亞引進的車型。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過這一系列與當初引進時相比，已經有了很大的變化。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只花短短三年就能夠做到這一步，喀蘭貿易在技術上的發展，令最早在此事上牽線的公爵閣下也頗為讚歎", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾希斯如果做不到，那為他力排眾議的恩希歐迪斯就該頭痛了。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你打算和我聊聊技術？", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你找錯人了，直接去找諾希斯聊，搞不好他還會有點興趣。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我很好奇，女士。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒想到會在這裡遇見您，還是在這樣的情況下。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是什麼人值得您親自出手？是多麼棘手的狀況，能讓您急迫到……沒有時間更換一雙沾滿血污的手套？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "解決了一點小麻煩。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勸你收起不合時宜的好奇心，“灰禮帽”。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是來找人的，暫時還不想再弄髒一雙手套。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無意冒犯。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我絕無干涉鐧女士行動的意思。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，想必在車上的一定是位重要人物……", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是又如何？", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您不介意透露些許，或許我能為您效勞。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟“尋人”……這也算是我們的日常工作之一。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好像搞錯了什麼。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯默許你們在他身邊探頭探腦，那是他的事，我不會管。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我沒那麼好的耐心。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道謝拉格比卡西米爾好在哪嗎？", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡冷是冷了點，相對的，蟲子就少一些。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些讓人心煩的飛蟲，總是讓人有伸手碾死的衝動。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收斂點，否則，我不介意替恩希歐迪斯動手。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……多謝忠告。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是警告。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，廢話夠多了。你拖夠時間了？", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很巧，我要找的就是剛剛在車廂門後面偷聽的那位。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#8$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g2_trainwalkway", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐧女士——", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_janttck_03", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_janshth", "delay": 0.8}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_slash_02_l", "x": 50.0, "y": 220.0, "rox": 55.0, "roy": 89.0, "roz": 50.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一道森冷白光在他的話說完前自眼前掠過。"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“灰禮帽”的阻擋被壓回腹中，他頭頂標誌性禮帽的帽簷無聲裂開，躲藏在偽裝之下的公爵密探終於露出驚懼的一角。"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女人的手狀似隨意地搭在鐧上。她的目光讓“灰禮帽”清晰地意識到——"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此刻，自己正是猛獸眼中的獵物。"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是很想讓這輛列車報廢。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別讓我說第二次。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓開。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者你想躺下讓路，也可以。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g2_trainwalkway", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_trainlp", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs2"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs2", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（開玩笑吧？！）", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#8$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（黑騎士，真是……如果是在卡西米爾，手上沾血的黑騎士可是能被印成珍稀隱藏閃卡的！）", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#8$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不光是“灰禮帽”，現在連黑騎士都出現在這趟列車上……？）", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#8$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（啊，還要加上我——一位維多利亞子爵，被黑騎士點名要找的重要人物。這真是群星薈萃！了不起！）", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#8$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（……）", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#8$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我需要現在立刻有人來告訴我這是即興娛樂，是個玩笑……我很需要！）", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#8$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "里斯本？", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要你現在立刻去確認喀蘭貿易有沒有異動——", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不對，先確認我們的人是否安全！", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的人？在營地的都沒問題，送你去車站後我們正常返回，沒有遭遇什麼異常狀況。", "name": "老練的士兵"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過傑弗遜他們拼酒還沒回來……我現在就讓人聯絡他們。", "name": "老練的士兵"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，哈洛德，聽你的語氣，出狀況了？", "name": "老練的士兵"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暫時沒事。暫時。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願是我想太多……", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#3$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，先確認傑弗遜他們現在的狀態，讓他們立刻報告！就算是醉死了，也給我爬起來應一聲再死！", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……行，我立刻辦。", "name": "老練的士兵"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……唉。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德在上，如果真像謝拉格人說的那樣，耶拉岡德無所不知，無處不在——", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看，現在就是您該顯顯靈的時候啦。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別把一個誠心的觀光客往外推啊。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬一最後做不成好客人，那我可就只能當個不受歡迎的惡客囉。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g2_trainwalkway", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_trainlp", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs3"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs3", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "目前就是這樣了。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡訊號有點問題，我試了下，車廂裡基本上接不到通訊，走道上還稍微好點。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸好之前拜託極光她們做了點準備，要不然估計還聯絡不上你們。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能有什麼事？放心，我好得很。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦！本艦就交給你們聯絡，幫我和其他人也問聲好！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就這樣，先掛了。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣應該就沒問題了……", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#11$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅莎琳！", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 25.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇啊！！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#14$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是、是你啊大叔，嚇了我一跳……", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#6$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在跑什麼？躲誰？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很抱歉，不過現在不是說這個的好時候。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#16$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅莎琳，你怎麼不待在包廂裡？", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#16$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，我出來透透氣。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼問題？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔沒有，透透氣當然沒有問題。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是——", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g2_trainwalkway", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……可惜，看來沒有太多解釋的時間了。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅莎琳，你先回包廂——不，等等，不行，“灰禮帽”那傢伙已經見過你了。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（而且，那傢伙說的“眼熟”……）", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“灰禮帽”？是說剛剛你那個戴帽子的同事？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，沒錯，就是他！", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我遇到一些小麻煩，羅莎琳。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "提前申明，將你捲入其中絕非我的本意，只不過……", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我不在，讓一些奇怪的人找到機會跟你搭訕就不好了。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？搭訕？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#6$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那種無聊的人別理就好了，要是還敢糾纏不休，就對著鼻子給他一拳！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#5$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不錯的辦法，之後有機會請務必這樣做。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過總有些就算挨了年輕小姐的拳頭，也不會輕易退卻的難纏的傢伙……", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我想邀請你，羅莎琳。要不要一起去最前方的餐車，品嚐蜂蜜飲料，順便迴避一些纏人的搭訕者？", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，你的意思是，一起去喝點蜂蜜飲料？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，我們去喝點蜂蜜飲料。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不是還要一路跑過去？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#5$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，是的，一路跑過去。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#4$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，大叔，後面追你的人快過來了吧，我都聽到腳步聲了！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#5$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還真是一點都不遮掩。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說過的，我不對女士說謊。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啊，雖然不知道你們在搞什麼名堂……", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但好像蠻有意思的，我跟了！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "榮幸之至。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼事不宜遲——", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，立刻，讓我們跑起來！", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#13$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}